---
title: Seared Chicken, Garlic Crouton & Roast Veggie Salad with Aioli Dressing & Caramelised Onion
description: You’re not going to believe how simple it is to make this Caesar-style salad yourself, from crunchy croutons to creamy aioli and tender chicken, topped with sharp Parmesan cheese. Once you’ve got this baby down, soggy supermarket salads will be a distant memory.
